Basic Comment Mentor Installation
=================================

[Summary]

This file contains both installation and removal instructions for COMTOR.

Comment Mentor has two major deployment cases. The first is a command-line
version, which is somewhat less involved to install and deploy. The second
is a web application that requires some web server setup.

[Short Version, Command Line]

 1) unpack comtor.tar.gz (if you are reading this file, you probably did so)
 2) cd comtor/
 3) cd code/
 4) ant

[Long Version, Command Line]

[Short Version, Web Application]

 1) Unpack comtor.tar.gz (if you are reading this file, you probably did so)
 2) Visit the install directory in your browser and follow the on-screen instructions.

[Long Version, Web Application]
